  "text": "In [CITATION_1] , we defined a domain for over-approximation of real values based on these forms with real coefficients. The concretizationΓ (x) ofx is a proper interval obtained by the evaluation of expression (2) with proper intervals ε i = [−1, 1] and classical interval arithmetic :",
